501c3: OTSF is a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization, and all U.S. donations are tax-deductible. We rely on support from donations and voluntary license fees for operational expenses.
nonprofit: The Open Transit Software Foundation (OTSF) is a non-profit organization dedicated to open source transit software and technology, initially formed in order to provide governance for the OneBusAway project.

Our members include government agencies, educational institutions, companies, non-profits, and individual contributors. A stable governance system ensures the reliability and longevity of our projects.
